attributes.Long form description: The student begins by changing the joy controllers to the comfort grip, when he finishes the student waits for new instructions. The instructor tells that he need no change the comfort grip to the Joy-con strap after that the student placed back the joycons on the Nintendo Switch and stand it using the kickstand, then he exchange de game cartridge and the sd card to finally turn on and off the Nintendo switch.

Now please place the red and blue controllers on the Joy-con comfort grip.
It's the biggest object you have on the table.
Great.
Now please change the controllers from the Joy-con comfort grip to the two Joy-con straps.
